movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: What's the hype about?
review: Let me begin by saying that I have seen all the other currently released Star Wars movies. However, when I sat down to watch Episode 1, I was unable to sit all the way through it! It seemed so boring, and the inclusion of Jar Jar Binks did not help it, either. It was thoroughly uninspiring. Episode 2, however, was different...
